<br>
Invis up, zone in<br>
Get wiped out by idiot_01 who is too dumb to stand and die<br>
Invis up, zone in and leave a few more corpses.<br>
Rinse and repeat...<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Hope that CT is up so IC or HL will come clear the zone for you so you can get your corpses.<br>
